rows.label: qst610302_msg0001
rows.name:
Ahhh, view from here is, as one say,
bomb. Haihabaiha luuurv looking down on
bustly-bustly factory floor!

rows.label: qst610302_msg0002
rows.name:
Haihabaiha wish Haihabaiha could stay
to watch factory work forevah...

rows.label: qst610302_msg0003
rows.name:
But on other wing, watch silent factory
floor after shift is over is also toppest
of notch...

rows.label: qst610302_msg0004
rows.name:
To cut to chase, Haihabaiha wish to remain
looking down on factory in all states of
busyness, twenty-four hour each day!

rows.label: qst610302_msg0005
rows.name:
Mehmeh?!
Now friends mention, Haihabaiha did come
here as part of tour, that right...

rows.label: qst610302_msg0006
rows.name:
That mean that reverie of Haihabaiha must
come to close sometime or other...

rows.label: qst610302_msg0007
rows.name:
No no, it okay. Haihabaiha know good thing
never last forever. Haihabaiha go quietly,
rejoin guide Toutour now.

rows.label: qst610302_msg0008
rows.name:
Thank you for reminding Haihabaiha about
hard facts of life.
